---
title: Sichuan Garlic Plant-Based Mince Tacos with Slaw & Coriander
description: Sichuan and garlic have come together in a deal to create tacos that no one can refuse. They are giving plant-based mince a new lease on life and the sesame seeds help to seal the deal. If you read the fine print, it’s guaranteed that these tacos will have everyone at your table feeling full and satisfied.

